Pod-Weaver-Section-AllowOverride version 0.02, released June 6, 2012


This section plugin for Pod::Weaver will allow you to override a
section normally provided by Pod::Weaver with a custom version in your
POD.



INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install



DEPENDENCIES

  Package                         Minimum Version
  ------------------------------- ---------------
  perl                             5.010
  Moose                            
  Moose::Util::TypeConstraints     
  Pod::Weaver::Role::Section       
  Pod::Weaver::Role::Transformer   
  namespace::autoclean



CHANGES
    Here's what's new in version 0.02 of Pod-Weaver-Section-AllowOverride:
    (See the file "Changes" for the full revision history.)

	- Add the action attribute



